{"tid":2198881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"知唔知道好多手足等緊你嘅信？佢哋先可以睇到連登同新聞！齊做寫信師！","createTime":"2020-09-11T16:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T15:10:55.000Z","uid":272572,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"430201b9da0b8618bb944976db4eef90c68cd5ed","tid":2198881,"uid":272572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0rQMrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0rQMrA.jpg&h=cadb5d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">端傳媒&mdash;《監獄高牆之下，寫信師寫給被囚示威者的一封封信》節錄：</span></strong><br />\n原文link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200910-hongkong-pen-pals-prison-prosecution/?fbclid=IwAR1569nttVLGT0M9-3T_azSh1ScDhE70NbkVUSxS3FahYQv3thktLv6OsN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200910-hongkong-pen-pals-prison-prosecution%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1569nttVLGT0M9-3T_azSh1ScDhE70NbkVUSxS3FahYQv3thktLv6OsN8&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=093a78aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200910-hongkong-pen-pals-prison-prosecution/?fbclid=IwAR1569nttVLGT0M9-3T_azSh1ScDhE70NbkVUSxS3FahYQv3thktLv6OsN8</a><br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span class=\"red\">20多歲的子勇（化名）因參與反修例運動，在香港的收押所羈押大半年了。</span></strong>每日生活千篇一律：早上7點半起床，晚上10點關燈，三餐以外，就是看書、看電視、做運動。冬天捱過了，夏天特別難熬。在囚者統統赤裸上身，一日沖涼四、五次，有時候子勇晚上悶熱得無法入睡。<br />\n<br />\n2. 「第二日起身再loop過（再輪迴）⋯⋯ 坦白講，什麼都慣了。」2020年晚夏，我們輾轉採訪到子勇，他說，<strong><span class=\"red\">「少數會變的，只有電視節目、探訪及家書，所以對這些不期然都有種期待。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3. 那些信件，<span class=\"red\"><strong>子勇說，他在收押所等待開庭的日子裏翻看又翻看，陪他走過很多個無眠夜。子勇珍惜每一封來信，「要知道現在這個年代，要坐定定寫封信是一件好奢侈的事。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 他說平均每星期會收到10封信，來自親友和陌生人，羈押至今，陌生人的信件估算有過百封，去年聖誕節還收到700多張聖誕卡。<span class=\"red\"><strong>「收到一刻好開心，覺得出面有很多人關心自己」</strong></span>，當下先草草看一次，返回房間後再三細讀，兩日內就會回覆有留下聯絡方法的信件。<br />\n<br />\n5. 在鐵窗之內，<span class=\"red\"><strong>子勇說，信函「可以無限次拎上手睇」（可以無限次拿在手中讀），是情緒低落的安慰劑，陪他走過許多個失眠的晚上</strong></span>。「睡不著有時會摷返啲信（找回信件），由第一封睇到最近一封，每次（看）不同人。」<br />\n<br />\n6. <span class=\"red\"><strong>這些信息，來自為在囚者提供牆外資訊包的「解悶工廠」</strong></span>。「工廠」位於立法會議員朱凱廸的辦事處，朱的研究幹事蔡雪華就是「廠長」，「生產線」上其餘兩個核心成員，包括「義工A」（化名）和「小妹」（化名）。<br />\n<br />\n7. 蔡雪華介紹說，這個工廠每日整理一冊資訊，一冊是至少10張A4紙，雙面壓縮列印，資訊豐富，包括每日的網媒報道和網絡熱話，因為懲教署可能會以版權為由抽走一些印有新聞報道的信件，<span class=\"red\"><strong>他們便用日誌的形式，把新聞變成一封信。「把它（資訊包）變成一封信」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n8. 有協助工廠的年輕義工憶起，一名在囚者曾向立法會議員求助，希望對方為自己爭取一包份量大一些的薯片。<span class=\"red\"><strong>「裏面的世界，人的需要就變得──你不可以說是簡單或trivial（微不足道），但這就是他生活的所有。」這個年輕義工認為，「你能夠給他一點資訊，讓他不至於與外面的世界脫節，也支撐了很多坐緊的手足的意志。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n9. 「我不想手足覺得：我上庭了但無人理。他也想知道世界如何報道這些case。」在周末及公眾假期，義工A會稍息，留待下一個工作日一併處理數天的資訊，幾年來從未間斷。<br />\n<br />\n10. <span class=\"red\"><strong>「我改善不到那張被，改善不到他沖涼，改善不到食飯，改善不到迫住看CCTVB（編按：香港網民惡搞稱翡翠台TVB為CCTVB，目前在香港監獄，在囚者一般只看到TVB），那我做些可能幫手的事。」她說。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">朝雲&mdash;《點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？全靠解悶工廠的義務工人》節錄：</span></strong><br />\n原文link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1616888655116740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003868649005%2Fposts%2F1616888655116740&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=9c238594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1616888655116740</a><br />\n<br />\n1. <span class=\"red\"><strong>「唔係話好沉重嘅工作量，但就係好長期嘅工作。」</strong></span>由於有一條流水線分工，過程枯燥而重覆，眾義工遂自嘲為「解悶工廠」。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span class=\"red\"><strong>梁天琦是「解悶工廠」的收信人之一，所以他會見到連登繼續討論他。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 原屬草創的解悶工廠結業無期，不是說五到十年，而是二三十年，可能一生一世仍未見到終點，到時點算？「未諗喎，到時先算。唔係剩係我一個，好多人都堅持緊，咁咪繼續做囉。」<span class=\"red\"><strong>她好擔心在囚者已習慣收到工廠來信，若突然再無音訊，會以為世界忘記了他們。「對於一個被困住嘅人嚟講，定時定候嘅 connection 好重要。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"navy\">【做寫信師方法及相關資料】</span></span></strong><br />\n　<br />\n1. 燕子生命 十年抗爭支援<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/swallowlife\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fswallowlife&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c18c644e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/swallowlife</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2146189/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2146189/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 邵家臻&mdash;「和你做筆友」計劃 Q&amp;A<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1316633175189330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fposts%2F1316633175189330&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=1749d33a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1316633175189330</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/2899076716851484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F2899076716851484%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=6100e626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/2899076716851484/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 被捕人士關注組 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/16722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F16722&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=cff37835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/16722</a> <br />\n<br />\n另外有手足填咗首「解悶工廠」歌，請支持吓<br />\n李芷君 Ada Lee - 《解悶工廠》 (Official Lyrics Video)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=31fClz9Ig-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D31fClz9Ig-s&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3foR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=bfc95045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=31fClz9Ig-s</a>"},{"pid":"58825b1cfd617e96611534129995db9307612c83","tid":2198881,"uid":272572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBkxZRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBkxZRY.jpg&h=e8afe588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNfNOLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNfNOLi.jpg&h=1001681f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivUCrwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivUCrwZ.jpg&h=24ce21ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wz65Aqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWz65Aqj.jpg&h=e271bce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨近中秋，不如大家都做寫信師，幫手足打打氣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab43443ee94dd83a05ed251d7ffc70cf9a805d07","tid":2198881,"uid":272572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce469790fe58ce98ef01cf6665cb0b38d0d7aa16","tid":2198881,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024dbd6ccd538c2c31f02a46afe5de133a2bf76a","tid":2198881,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817ab00293ed849c5de0f4390389798719f666c0","tid":2198881,"uid":272572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T17:00:13.000Z"